{"tid":1909494,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"「樓價跟本無跌過」","createTime":"2020-03-04T04:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T09:14:55.000Z","uid":19725,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"39cb378aaa3621620fca191a90ccbf250277056f","tid":1909494,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T04:07:42.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情持續，直接影響市場氣氛，有業主蝕讓離場，其中元朗世宙1座高層A室，面積646方呎，三房連士多房間隔，原先叫價920萬元，經議價後以848萬元易手，減幅約8%，折合呎價13,127元。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，原業主於2016年以約889萬元購入，持貨約4年帳面損失約41萬元離場。<br />\n<br />\n不過，土地註冊處資料顯示，原業主當年購入單位時，需要支付樓價7.5%的雙倍印花稅，涉約66萬元，再計及佣金等雜項支出，估計實際損手逾115萬元離場。<br />\n<br />\n唔計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4d755e4d3985ae967f439d05e556b7231e7521","tid":1909494,"uid":19092,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T04:32:17.000Z","msg":"AA:個別業主持貨力低， 唔影響樓價，所以唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登話升就升， 廢淡唔洗指意執死雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163a2e9a5d47b884b6d55734de09499a2883c83a","tid":1909494,"uid":337986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:04:41.000Z","msg":"樓價就好似個股市咁<br />\n無論點都唔會跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d8cad724607c3d4a6711082cf245cb180e1133","tid":1909494,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"163a2e9a5d47b884b6d55734de09499a2883c83a","tid":1909494,"uid":337986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:04:41.000Z","msg":"樓價就好似個股市咁<br />\n無論點都唔會跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:03:11.000Z","msg":"淡淡跌過幾% 又叫晒春 你有首期未呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成個藍絲咁為左層樓 真係好撚可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm